# 🛒 E-commerce Sales Dashboard (Power BI)

A comprehensive Power BI dashboard analyzing online retail performance including revenue trends, product category insights, and customer segmentation.

## 📊 Key Features
- Total Revenue, Orders, and Average Order Value (AOV)
- Category-wise Sales & Profit Breakdown
- Sales Trends by Month, Region, and Platform
- Customer Segment & Region Performance
- Return Rate and Order Fulfillment Analysis
- Interactive Slicers for Category, Region, Date, and Platform

## 📁 Files Included
- `Ecommerce_Sales.pbix` – Power BI report
- `ecommerce_data.xlsx` – Dataset used for analysis
- `dashboard_preview.png` – Screenshot of dashboard

## 🛠 Tools & Techniques
- Power BI Desktop
- DAX (for KPIs, profit margin calculations, etc.)
- Power Query (for data cleaning and transformation)

## 📷 Dashboard Preview

![Ecommerce Dashboard](dashboard_preview.png)

---

## 🎯 Use Case

Ideal for e-commerce analysts and business teams to:
- Track revenue and growth over time
- Identify best-selling product categories
- Improve customer segmentation and targeting
- Optimize regional sales performance
